{"tid":2375652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方指疫情導致「勒索保護費」近乎絕跡的舊式黑幫行為再度出現 共拘捕131人","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T08:45:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0790dc336919192204b31e2a4928d69413cb224b","tid":2375652,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"警方自去年12月中至今年1月中，展開反三合會行動，拘捕131人，他們涉嫌販毒、藏毒、非法經營賭博場所、走私及售賣未完稅香煙、藏有攻擊武器及違反限聚令等。<br />\n<br />\n警方估計有黑幫集團因疫情及警方打擊令收入大減，於是向菜檔、運輸工人及賣飯盒的小販勒索保護費，警方形容是近乎絕跡的舊式黑幫行為，已拘捕20人涉嫌勒索及刑事毀壞。<br />\n<br />\n警方說留意到疫情下經濟轉差，有黑幫份子招聘正在待業的南亞裔人士，並提供可觀報酬作販毒行為，早前在元朗一間鐵皮屋搗破一個懷疑販毒場所，拘捕3人，包括2名南亞人士，檢獲約值9萬元的懷疑可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方說去年底亦到屯門一處工廠大廈突擊搜查，相信由黑幫租用的3個無牌酒吧及一間派對場所，行動中拘捕71人，並以限聚令將他們票控，期間檢獲2000支烈酒及啤酒等。警方說，其中一間無牌酒吧面積僅約800呎，但有29人身處在內，內裡衛生情況惡劣，牆身有隔音棉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571810-20210122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571810-20210122.htm&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=c2a874ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571810-20210122.htm&h=ee0ab861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571810-20210122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"40009b3ee6bb06ab679ee8095e8a4e56a45d7477","tid":2375652,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3243fc9bbc209d33f031640ff2bb30a5693db8aa","tid":2375652,"uid":78243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"黑社會未交保護費俾黑警拉"},{"pid":"49ab53e5d999c68d44f0da36aeafea5f7f2bc7b9","tid":2375652,"uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"黑幫指疫情導致「收虧」近乎絕跡的舊式黑警行為再度出現"},{"pid":"0c8dfa7edf8362d4c0e1e8e139304f7acb7e2a4c","tid":2375652,"uid":185656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"佢哋學黑警經立法會勒索咪冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404b35d5bdaa46d4c8c26837483083ff0e1b380e","tid":2375652,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"同班狗自導自演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ae7f2752ad704b3ff6393a6a423ddc1ddfb2a0","tid":2375652,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"唔係近乎絕跡<br />\n係你唔撚做嘢"},{"pid":"b13eea423779aa4b27cfd0b23940866c2721d6e8","tid":2375652,"uid":3093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"警方<del>指疫情</del>導致「勒索保護費」舊式黑幫行為再度出現"},{"pid":"15f058628dceba137d0f8113549c2a4cd5505d4c","tid":2375652,"uid":32816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"好快就到運吉逗利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e378c139658525c2c1fada4b236079aa8063c0","tid":2375652,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊夠你599G 既保護費收得多呀"},{"pid":"b9bd05fa29ac65106507f035a89e00977d4970fb","tid":2375652,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sxsQAsNa2U0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsxsQAsNa2U0&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=13f66b4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sxsQAsNa2U0</a>"},{"pid":"2b5374ba241f60fcc8ca4b59f3c40f4f0537e3a5","tid":2375652,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite